{"tid":2088094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府又射哂納稅人既錢落海，泛民又有5個人關鍵缺席，9月仲投佢地？不如投票比棵樹啦","createTime":"2020-07-01T03:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T04:50:24.000Z","uid":60916,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2f21707731ea79d94e303fedcb69860c505ae419","tid":2088094,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:42:38.000Z","msg":"財委會通過撥款200億元予社署 購160個物業作社福用途<br />\n2020-06-30 16:55<br />\n<br />\n立法會財務委員會通過撥款200億元予社會福利署，在全港各區購買約160個物業，以提供福利設施。跨黨派議員關注當局沒有優先考慮採用政府閒置土地及處所，又指預算過高、無善用空置校舍。有議員擔心批出一筆過撥款後，日後無法監察。社署則承諾，每年將到立法會匯報購買物業的進展，亦會貼近市價購入物業，不會造成托市。//<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>缺席泛民議員包括：梁耀忠、涂謹申、李國麟、梁繼昌、郭榮鏗</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Few3h5O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFew3h5O.png&h=35f53df2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"082f13f8193ce447d52c3ffe43f815820ceb4081","tid":2088094,"uid":63822,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:43:11.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#60916 - 周俊樂(-10)</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請保持批判性思考，善用「上一頁」和「不推文回覆」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">該會員以往言論 (7)：</div><code>1 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eQijrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eQijrT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>2 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eBHfvT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eBHfvT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠, 做假新聞</span><br />\n<code>3 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eAEteT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eAEteT</a><span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<code>4 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/esqExT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/esqExT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>5 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/esqBmT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/esqBmT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">洗白黑警</span